document_data.name: Osco Salibuck
document_data.mainbody: '''Osco Salibuck the Elder''' was a male [[halfling]] and an associate of [[Khelben "Blackstaff" Arunsun]], and the ancestor of [[Osco Salibuck]].
document_data.History: He had a statue honoring his service to Khelben in [[Blackstaff Tower]]. His statue had a rather unpleasant expression, long hair, and carried a small [[scimitar]]. His ghost was impersonated by the ghost of Khelben in order to test young Osco Salibuck.
